class.comment: Utility class for handling with a bukkit @(org.bukkit.Art) and a NMS @(net.minecraft.world.entity.decoration.PaintingVariant).

minecraftToBukkit.comment: Converts a NMS @(net.minecraft.world.entity.decoration.PaintingVariant) to a bukkit @(org.bukkit.Art).

minecraftHolderToBukkit.comment: Converts a holder of a NMS @(net.minecraft.world.entity.decoration.PaintingVariant) to a bukkit @(org.bukkit.Art).

bukkitToMinecraft.comment: Converts a bukkit @(org.bukkit.Art) to a NMS @(net.minecraft.world.entity.decoration.PaintingVariant).

bukkitToMinecraftHolder.comment: Converts a bukkit @(org.bukkit.Art) to a holder of a NMS @(net.minecraft.world.entity.decoration.PaintingVariant).
